\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n數又唔識計<br />\n股又唔識炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剩係識做五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老味改個名仲要抄鳩人<br />\n五毛黎講你都算垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLoser笑賺錢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c22296f3f0815872a4349cb851081b4eba1ece0","tid":2402220,"uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"多啲五毛入黎spin啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我厭未夠多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dff965dcad17efefb5098a90eccbe9c64ea605","tid":2402220,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"創辦人都好可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n聲網另外可疑之處，是其創辦人的由Webex張開的關係網。聲網創辦人兼CEO趙斌，和Zoom創辦人兼CEO袁征，都曾是WebEx的工程師。袁征是Frontend R&amp;D Lead，而趙斌可說是現在的Full-stack兼管前後端。<br />\n<br />\n  而WebEx的Co-founder朱敏，在文革期間經歷過上山下鄉，改革開放後，被中共派到Stanford留學，其後1996年聯合創辦Webex，四年後上市。<br />\n<br />\n  雖然WebEx現在是Cisco的，不過是在2007收購而來。WebEx其實可說是第一代中國滲透美國矽谷的公司。只是當時中美關係融洽，期待中國改革開放後會「民主化」，對此類公司完全沒有戒心。<br />\n<br />\n  加上這些工程師背景的中國技術間諜政治色彩淡薄，矽谷一度對這些來追美國夢「技術宅」非常受落。<br />\n<br />\n  WebEx Mafia橫跨中美的諜網 <br />\n  但WebEx一開始就是一間不折不扣的中國公司。而其早期團隊，都由中國招聘去美國，當中就包括趙斌和袁征兩人。<br />\n  由袁征創辦並管理的Zoom，屢屢爆出秘密泄露資料予中共的安全問題，連台灣政府都禁用。兩間公司都是在美國和大陸兩邊開辦公室，而且在中國僱用大量工程師，而聲網更加有大量中國生意連繫，說這間公司不會比Zoom與中共更合作，你真的會相信嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60201698ae11380f2f6e2be4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F60201698ae11380f2f6e2be4&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=49d302c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/60201698ae11380f2f6e2be4</a>"},{"pid":"dd77e1cdfef07f40cee3979a788285522bc1cc35","tid":2402220,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3a30df55cf90053eacc8e1922a57d1f03cec650","tid":2402220,"uid":253608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"信支那野真係死得人<br />\n希望班新疆人唔好因為咁而瀨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"引蛇出洞係支那好拿手"},{"pid":"ed8063b432e3ddad298b342d5e2e121b868f3517","tid":2402220,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"而家先知clubhouse同zoom兩兄弟"},{"pid":"6d47c42fd9b7127d8ed829d843bc5fdb67e4822b","tid":2402220,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed8063b432e3ddad298b342d5e2e121b868f3517","tid":2402220,"uid":64745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"而家先知clubhouse同zoom兩兄弟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6c7e774995690920ef8637b8ce46cd9815e8be","tid":2402220,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9dff965dcad17efefb5098a90eccbe9c64ea605","tid":2402220,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"創辦人都好可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n聲網另外可疑之處，是其創辦人的由Webex張開的關係網。聲網創辦人兼CEO趙斌，和Zoom創辦人兼CEO袁征，都曾是WebEx的工程師。袁征是Frontend R&amp;D Lead，而趙斌可說是現在的Full-stack兼管前後端。<br />\n<br />